a=\left(\frac{Z\,M}{\rho\,N_A}\right)^{1/3}
\]

Insert the data ( \(M = 168.4\;\mathrm{g\,mol^{-1}},\; \rho = 3.988\;\mathrm{g\,cm^{-3}},\;
N_A = 6.022\times10^{23}\;\mathrm{mol^{-1}}\) ):

\[
